n, k = map(int, input().split())
fr = [0]*(n+1)
ta = [0]*(n+1)
for i in range(1, n+1):
    fr[i] = i - 1
    ta[i] = i + 1
while k > 0:
    op, x = map(int, input().split())
    if op == 1:
        if x != n:
            fr[ta[x]] = fr[x]
        ta[fr[x]] = ta[x]
        ta[x] = -1
        fr[x] = -1
    else:
        print(fr[x])
    k -= 1
